{"id":278573,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/02/维权网-半夜枪击村民卧室，书记入室毒打老妪/","date":"2013-02-09T06:15:42Z","modified":"2013-02-09T06:15:42Z","title":"维权网 | 半夜枪击村民卧室，书记入室毒打老妪——杭州滨江区发生一起罕见的强拆事件（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员萧风报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>日下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>时</span><span>左右，居住在杭州市滨江区的韩张良一家人正在家里休息，家中突然闯入六七个人，带头的是村干部林昌，进门就扬言是来闹事的，一进门就大吵大闹，韩家人立即拿出手机拍照，走在最前面的那个人一把夺过手机，使劲摔出门外，外面的其他几个跟从人员拼命的用脚踩摔在地上的手机，致致手机破裂、报废。随后这些人又闯入家中踢门摔凳。韩家立刻报了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">110</span><span>，在等待</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">110</span><span>的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>多分钟时间里，这群人扬言说，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">110</span><span>来了我们也不怕，我们就在这里等</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">110</span><span>，你们再敢拍照，我们还要摔，还要仍。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">110</span><span>来了，但并没有立案。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>日</span><span>凌晨</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>时左右，村民们正在梦乡中，突然被一声声枪声惊醒，原来有人拿着步枪对韩家二楼韩张良儿子韩忠夫妻的卧室射击。韩忠夫妇从睡梦中惊醒，吓得灯也不敢开。他们从后面窗户望出去，发现在信诚路上有两个男人在朝他们卧室床头的玻璃窗开枪。韩忠大喝一声：“你们干什么？”那两个人钻进一辆小轿车后，逆向行驶向滨盛路方向逃走了。随后韩忠发现床头玻璃上有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>个被子弹南穿的破洞，在现场找到了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>颗子弹。他们立即打</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">110</span><span>报警。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">110</span><span>到来后，拍了照片，了解了一下事情经过就走了。当时接警的警官</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span><span>警号</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">112819)</span><span>只是叫他们白天去长河派出所做笔录。他们去了长河派出所，接待他们的警官</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span><span>警号</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">112523)</span><span>只是叫他们自己写了一下事情经过，没给做笔录，根本就没立案。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>日</span><span>上午韩忠夫妇再次上派出所，坚持要警方给一个不立案的理由，派出所才立了案</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span><span>接受案件回执单受理编号</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">01081352151)</span><span>。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>日</span><span>，杭州市国土资源局滨江分局又发了杭土滨监字</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">(2013</span><span>）第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">120354</span><span>号限期拆除非法占地上的违法建筑通知书，要拆韩家的房子。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>日</span><span>凌晨</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>时左右，又有一群不明身份的男人</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span><span>大概有七八个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span><span>，每人手持铁棍，将韩家一楼的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>块铝合金玻璃门敲破，地上一片狼藉，现场还留下一根铁棍，当晚浙江省电视“</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1818</span><span>黄金眼”播报了韩家的这段新闻。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">31</span><span>日</span><span>，江三村党书记孔先忠和村长何国强、村妇女主任来国梅等人来到韩家。韩家因屡受骚扰，自己制作了来客登记表，要求村干部填写。村干部拒绝填写，双方发生争执，村书记孔先忠狠狠地将韩忠近</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">70</span><span>岁的母亲毒打了一顿。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>日</span><span>，政府在没有任何书面告知，签字的情况下，村长何国强、村妇女主任来国梅、村干部卫江以及一大批身穿警服、便衣的几百人包围了韩家，将他们一家人关在家中，每个门口都有七八个身强力壮的男人守门，不让他们出来，在光天化日之下扒掉了韩家的房子。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">21</span><span>日</span><span>国务院颁布的《国有土地上房屋征收与补偿条例》第三十五条明确规定：“本条例自公布之日起施行。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2001</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>日</span><span>国务院公布的《城市房屋拆迁管理条例》同时废止。本条例施行前已依法取得房屋拆迁许可证的项目，继续沿用原有的规定办理，但政府不得责成有关部门强制拆迁。”也就是说，《国有土地上房屋征收与补偿条例》已明令禁止对公民私有房屋的强拆行为。但是，浙江省杭州市滨江区政府公然蔑视国务院的禁令，于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>日</span><span>出动几百人，将该区长河街道江三村十区</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">56</span><span>号村民韩张良的房屋强行拆除。为了迫使韩家就范，街道和村干部使尽了种种卑劣、下流的手段，三年多来一直对韩家进行胁迫、恐吓、骚扰，今年年初到了登峰造极的地步，竟雇佣一批流氓地痞在半夜两点钟用步枪对韩家二楼卧室的窗户进行射击，同时还用铁棍对韩家一楼的大门和窗户猛砸，将韩家的玻璃打得粉碎。在一连几天骚扰没有使韩家屈服后，村书记亲自上门，对韩张良近</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">70</span><span>岁的妻子拳脚相加，党官狰狞的面目暴露无遗。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2009</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日</span><span>杭州市国土资源局给杭州市滨江区长河街道江三村经济合作社颁发杭滨土资拆许字</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">(2009</span><span>）第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>号房屋拆迁许可证，张贴拆迁公告，要韩张良家于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2009</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日</span><span>至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>日</span><span>拆迁期限，从此韩家被列为拆迁户。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2009</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>日</span><span> </span><span>长河街道办事处对韩家发出了限期拆除通知书</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span><span>长河限拆字</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">(2009</span><span>）第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30073</span><span>号</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span><span>，诬称韩家的小房子是违章建筑，需要拆除，但没有任何书面文字认定那房子是违章建筑。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2010</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>日</span><span>杭州市滨江区政府发了强制拆除违法建筑决定书（滨强拆</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">(2010</span><span>）第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">015</span><span>号）。韩家随后向杭州市政府提出行政复议，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2010</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">16</span><span>日</span><span>，杭州市政府作出“杭政复决</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">(2010</span><span>）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">78</span><span>号”复议决定书，撤销了滨强拆</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">(2010</span><span>）第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">015</span><span>号。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2010</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日</span><span>杭州市滨江区政府再次作出强制拆除违法建筑决定书（滨强拆</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">(2010</span><span>）第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">020</span><span>号）。但韩家坚持认为滨江区政府违法，不予“配合”。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月底开始，政府因强拆没有法律依据，便动用黑白两道，交替对韩家进行骚扰、恐吓，逼迫韩家就范。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>日</span><span>，从来不对农村居民房屋进行消防检查的区消防队光临韩家，说他家消防不合格，抢走了他家租户的煤气瓶和煤气灶。随后，派出所又三天两头到他家查流动人口暂住证。各政府部门的种种手段没能达到目的，最后将韩张良一家非法限制自由，强行将其房屋拆除。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-fq-k2qP0i-M/URXbqiBC6OI/AAAAAAAAcfQ/Z2GZCFTUocs/s1600/1111111.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-fq-k2qP0i-M/URXbqiBC6OI/AAAAAAAAcfQ/Z2GZCFTUocs/s1600/1111111.jpg\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-K6y5Z6SDvM4/URXbsvavzTI/AAAAAAAAcfY/wnEIOvqqWcE/s1600/001.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-K6y5Z6SDvM4/URXbsvavzTI/AAAAAAAAcfY/wnEIOvqqWcE/s1600/001.jpg\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-YnygchF-_yQ/URXbs-PCVSI/AAAAAAAAcfg/kiErfa8RJlc/s1600/002_%E5%89%AF%E6%9C%AC.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-YnygchF-_yQ/URXbs-PCVSI/AAAAAAAAcfg/kiErfa8RJlc/s1600/002_%E5%89%AF%E6%9C%AC.jpg\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-DA6IjI14Mu0/URXbs-SH_8I/AAAAAAAAcfk/LuSxEolX4jY/s1600/006.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-DA6IjI14Mu0/URXbs-SH_8I/AAAAAAAAcfk/LuSxEolX4jY/s1600/006.jpg\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-jOsxn5d_S6U/URXbup3zwaI/AAAAAAAAcfw/AE_Fy2Mkfwg/s1600/201302041342.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-jOsxn5d_S6U/URXbup3zwaI/AAAAAAAAcfw/AE_Fy2Mkfwg/s1600/201302041342.jpg\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-e03VlZelMMI/URXbwZjn1fI/AAAAAAAAcf4/pAbgSjBoSRs/s1600/201302041457.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-e03VlZelMMI/URXbwZjn1fI/AAAAAAAAcf4/pAbgSjBoSRs/s1600/201302041457.jpg\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-hfNWZ0ye6bc/URXbw4IjFpI/AAAAAAAAcgA/3Q6MPiJKnOY/s1600/201302041414.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-hfNWZ0ye6bc/URXbw4IjFpI/AAAAAAAAcgA/3Q6MPiJKnOY/s1600/201302041414.jpg\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-B-29NmaIiBw/URXbxoVb71I/AAAAAAAAcgI/Q-mjtytNijg/s1600/DSC_0030%5B(000450)22-34-24%5D.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-B-29NmaIiBw/URXbxoVb71I/AAAAAAAAcgI/Q-mjtytNijg/s1600/DSC_0030%5B(000450)22-34-24%5D.JPG\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-OAyrxFcmnYI/URXbx-P7iaI/AAAAAAAAcgM/HTGJpttyXdM/s1600/DSC_0030%5B(000866)22-20-20%5D.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-OAyrxFcmnYI/URXbx-P7iaI/AAAAAAAAcgM/HTGJpttyXdM/s1600/DSC_0030%5B(000866)22-20-20%5D.JPG\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-e_nf0_OmqkI/URXby8_bAvI/AAAAAAAAcgY/RYf80iHyec8/s1600/SAM_1784.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-e_nf0_OmqkI/URXby8_bAvI/AAAAAAAAcgY/RYf80iHyec8/s1600/SAM_1784.JPG\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-uaom0belhTI/URXb0FdiMHI/AAAAAAAAcgg/UtNkfjsdrBE/s1600/SAM_1809.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-uaom0belhTI/URXb0FdiMHI/AAAAAAAAcgg/UtNkfjsdrBE/s1600/SAM_1809.JPG\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,17850,20534],"tags":[28519,19196]}